Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: My Home
Description: An awesome little duplex in Isla Vista with a big yard and great roommates and neighbors!

Name: My Mom's House
Description: A beautiful, old victorian era house in the Bernal Heights neighborhood of San Francisco. It is where I grew up.

Name: Yosemite Valley
Description: The viewpoint from the entrance to Yosemite valley, one of the most beautiful places I have ever been.

Name: Mayo's Carniceria
Description: My favorite taqueria in Santa Barbara. Their meat is amazing and their salsa and tortillas are made in-house.

Name: Montecito Hot Springs
Description: Man-made hot spring pool hidden back in the Montecito hills. Requires a short hike in but is very worth it!
